title: DDFP 286: Week 1 preview
itunes:title: DDFP 286: Week 1 preview
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank and "Around the NFL" podcast host Dan Hanzus to preview the Packers vs. Seahawks and the rest of the NFL's 2014 opening week. Plus, Shek and Daniel Jeremiah discuss coaches to watch in the 2014 season with Brian Billick from "The Coaches Show" podcast.  

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
